org.intellimate.izou.system.sound

Class SoundManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.intellimate.izou.IzouModule
      • org.intellimate.izou.system.sound.SoundManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AddonThreadPoolUser, EventsControllerModel, Identifiable, MainProvider

    public class SoundManager
extends IzouModule
implements AddonThreadPoolUser, EventsControllerModel
    the SoundManager manages all IzouSoundLine, tracks them and is responsible for enforcing that only one permanent- AddOn can play at one time.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    LeanderK
